# Generated data: saved posterior draws and derived tables
# (regenerate deterministically from the week scripts). The two raw
# returns series are tracked as the frozen inputs of the whole project,
# since Yahoo revises its history silently.
week*/data/*
!week4/data/sp500_returns.csv
!week8/data/sp500_returns_ext.csv

# Word renders of the writeups live outside the repo; only markdown is tracked
*.docx

# The docx generator scripts stay out of the repo too (they depend on the
# md2docx renderer at the project root, which is not part of the repo)
week*/code/generate_week*_doc.py

# Week 9 final report held back until it is ready; files kept locally
week9/
